Beautiful, updated one-bedroom apartment in North Park. Conveniently located within walking distance of shopping, restaurants, entertainment, libraries and Balboa Park. Downtown, Coronado and our famous beaches are only minutes away. Call today to schedule your tour.

~ Ceiling fan
~ Wall-to-Wall closet
~ Online application and rent payment
~ Security deposit $750.00 OAC
~ Six and 12 month-leases
~ All utilities paid by residents
